data.description: Welcome to this wonderful 1930s 4-bedroom home with delightful features and modern updates! The original hardwoods, updated windows, and electric make this home a blend of vintage charm and modern comfort. Coved ceilings, arched entryways and glass door knobs just to name a few. The huge unfinished basement provides potential for customization and additional living or storage space. Just steps outside you will enjoy flowering trees, garden spaces and the generous back yard provides great outdoor areas for entertaining, grilling, and relaxation. The location close to the shipyard, Seattle ferry, shopping and more adds to the home's appeal, making it convenient and accessible for various activities and amenities.
